<span id="Structure_toolbar"></span>
===Panel nástrojů Struktura===

* [[File:Std_Part.svg|32px]] [[Std_Part|Nový díl]]: Vytvoří novou součást a aktivuje ji.

* <span id="Part_Datums">[[File:Part_CoordinateSystem.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Souřadnice: {{Version|1.1}}</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_Datums pages redirect here-->

:* [[File:Part_CoordinateSystem.svg|32px]] [[Part_CoordinateSystem|Souřadnicový systém]]: Vytvoří objekt souřadnicového systému, který lze připojit k jiným objektům. {{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumPlane.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumPlane|Referenční rovina]]: Vytvoří objekt referenční roviny, který lze připojit k jiným objektům. {{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumLine.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumLine|Referenční linie]]: Vytvoří objekt referenční linky, který lze připojit k jiným objektům. {{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumPoint.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumPoint|Referenční bod]]: Vytvoří objekt referenčního bodu, který lze připojit k jiným objektům. {{Version|1.1}}

* [[File:Std_Group.svg|32px]] [[Std_Group|Nová skupina]]: Vytvoří novou skupinu.

* <span id="Std_LinkActions">[[File:Std_LinkMake.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Akce odkazu:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Std_LinkActions pages redirect here-->

:* [[File:Std_LinkMake.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMake|Vytvořit odkaz]]: Vytvoří odkaz.

:* [[File:Std_LinkMakeRelative.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMakeRelative|Vytvořit pododkaz]]: Vytvoří odkaz na podobjekt nebo podprvek.

:* [[File:Std_LinkReplace.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkReplace|Nahradit za odkaz]]: Nahradí objekt(y) novým odkazem (odkazy).

:* [[File:Std_LinkUnlink.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkUnlink|Zrušit propojení]]: Náhradí odkazy jejich propojenými objekty.

:* [[File:Std_LinkImport.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkImport|Importovat odkaz]]: Importuje vybrané externí odkazy.

:* [[File:Std_LinkImportAll.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkImportAll|Importovat všechny odkazy]]: Importuje všechny externí odkazy.

* [[File:Std_VarSet.svg|32px]] [[Std_VarSet|Variable Set]]: Creates a set of properties that can be used as variables in [[Expressions|expressions]]. {{Version|1.0}}

===Additional tools===

* [[File:Std_LinkMakeGroup.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMakeGroup|Link Group]]: Creates a group of links.

* [[Std_Expressions|Expression Actions]]:

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_Selected|Copy Selected]]: Copies expression data from selected objects to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_Active_Document|Copy Active Document]]: Copies expression data from the active document to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_All_Documents|Copy All Documents]]: Copies expression data from all documents to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Paste|Paste]]: Pastes expression data from the Clipboard.

* [[Image:Part_SelectFilter.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter|Selection Filter]]: {{Version|1.0}}

:* [[Image:Vertex-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Vertex_Selection|Vertex Selection]]: Only allows the selection of vertices.

:* [[Image:Edge-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Edge_Selection|Edge Selection]]: Only allows the selection of edges.

:* [[Image:Face-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Face_Selection|Face Selection]]: Only allows the selection of faces.

:* [[Image:Clear-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#No_Selection_Filters|No Selection Filters]]: Allows the selection of all subelements.

* [[File:Std_TreeSelectAllInstances.svg|32px]] [[Std_TreeSelectAllInstances|Select All Instances]]: Selects all instances of an object in the [[Tree_View|Tree View]].

* [[File:Std_ToggleFreeze.svg|32px]] [[Std_ToggleFreeze|Toggle Freeze]]: Toggles the freeze state of objects. {{Version|1.0}}

===Obsolete tools===

* [[File:Std_FreeCADFAQ.svg|32px]] [[Std_FreeCADFAQ|FreeCAD FAQ]]: Opens the FreeCAD FAQ wiki page. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[File:Std_FreeCADPowerUserHub.svg|32px]] [[Std_FreeCADPowerUserHub|Python scripting documentation]]: Opens the FreeCAD Power users documentation wiki page. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[File:Std_OnlineHelp.svg|32px]] [[Std_OnlineHelp|Help]]: Opens the help documentation. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[Image:Std_MeasureDistance.svg|32px]] [[Std_MeasureDistance|Measure distance]]: Creates an object to measure and display a distance. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.

* [[Image:View_Measure_Clear_All.svg|32px]] [[View_Measure_Clear_All|Clear measurement]]: Clears [[Part_Workbench|Part]]  measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.

* [[Image:View_Measure_Toggle_All.svg|32px]] [[View_Measure_Toggle_All|Toggle measurement]]: Toggles the display of Part measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.


